\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

 and a closed set 
\begin_inset Formula $F\subseteq E$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $f=g$
\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

 and 
